Preconditions:
- The input array `nums` is not null.
- The length of the input array `nums` is greater than or equal to 1.
- Each element in the input array `nums` is an integer.
- Each element in the input array `nums` is greater than or equal to 1.
- Each element in the input array `nums` is less than or equal to 10^5.

Postconditions:
- The return value is an integer.
- The return value is the sum of the widths of all the non-empty subsequences of the input array `nums`.
- The return value is modulo 10^9 + 7.